84
00:05:13.355 --> 00:05:15.267
So your team doesn't exist. all right?

85
00:05:15.524 --> 00:05:19.003
You'll be filtered into new ODAs
when the opportunities arise.

86
00:05:19.027 --> 00:05:22.191
