is our assigned region. sir.

91
00:05:29.287 --> 00:05:31.265
Really? I didn't know that!

92
00:05:31.289 --> 00:05:32.642
Here's the thing. though.
You don't have a region

93
00:05:32.666 --> 00:05:34.077
'cause you don't have a fucking team!

94
00:05:34.251 --> 00:05:37.271
So get back to your goddamn desk
and let me do my job!

95
00:05:37.295 --> 00:05:38.439
Fuck.

96
00:05:38.463 --> 00:05:39.920
Sergeant. who's on line four?

97
00:05:40.048 --> 00:05:43.402
<i>It was not long
before that tower collapsed.</i>

98
00:05:43.426 --> 00:05:49.033
