103
00:06:02.529 --> 00:06:06.551
<i>we believe this one to have been
a United Airlines flight.</i>

104
00:06:06.575 --> 00:06:08.441
<i>smashed into the Pentagon around 9:45...</i>

105
00:06:08.618 --> 00:06:09.762
Yo. What's up. Cap?

106
00:06:09.786 --> 00:06:10.902
What up. Milo?
What are you doing here?

107
00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:12.765
Trying to get my team back.

108
00:06:12.789 --> 00:06:15.031
Your little jalapeño ain't gonna be
too happy about that. huh?

109
00:06:15.292 --> 00:06:16.853
Yeah. maybe not.
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

110
00:06:16.877 --> 00:06:19.146
This team's done. And thanks to you.

111
00:06:19.170 --> 00:06:21.412
we're gonna be watching this whole thing
