126
00:06:50.201 --> 00:06:54.015
Fuck yeah. bro. Fuck yeah.
I mean. we would have been.

127
00:06:54.039 --> 00:06:55.496
If we had a fucking captain.

128
00:06:56.875 --> 00:06:59.208
We'll be in this fight. boys.
You mark my words.

129
