137
00:07:53.848 --> 00:07:56.135
you're cutting the head off
your most venomous snake. sir.

138
00:07:57.394 --> 00:07:58.384
Yeah.

139
00:07:59.104 --> 00:08:00.748
Okay.

140
00:08:00.772 --> 00:08:02.208
