205
00:13:14.794 --> 00:13:16.605
Don't salute in country.

206
00:13:16.629 --> 00:13:18.399
Are you trying to get
our captain killed. bro?

207
00:13:18.423 --> 00:13:19.914
These are all friendlies.

208
00:13:20.049 --> 00:13:21.110
Oh. yeah?

209
00:13:21.134 --> 00:13:23.091
Who. that guy? That's not my friend.

210
00:13:23.678 --> 00:13:25.010
And that guy's definitely not my friend.

211
00:13:25.471 --> 00:13:26.907
Fucking Diller. bro.

212
00:13:26.931 --> 00:13:28.263
I could be their friend. He looks nice.

213
00:13:28.433 --> 00:13:30.265
That guy?
Yeah.

214
00:13:31.686 --> 00:13:33.414
Heads up. Heads up.

215
00:13:34.772 --> 00:13:37.810
What's up. guys?
Looks like Christmas came early. huh?

216
00:13:38.318 --> 00:13:40.401
Oh. yeah. Ho. ho. ho.
Where have you guys been?

217
00:13:40.611 --> 00:13:42.506
Oh. we went to
