221
00:13:49.620 --> 00:13:51.140
Snowed last night. So get used to it.

222
00:13:51.164 --> 00:13:52.496
What? Really?
Yeah.

223
00:13:53.207 --> 00:13:54.268
Hey. what's all this?

224
